# Evaluation Controller Endpoints
# Base URL: http://localhost:3001
# Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Create evaluation (protected)
POST http://localhost:3001/evaluations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "internId": "<intern-id>",
  "mentorId": "<mentor-id>",
  "score": 0,
  "comments": "Initial evaluation"
}

### Get all evaluations (protected)
GET http://localhost:3001/evaluations
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Get evaluation by ID (protected)
GET http://localhost:3001/evaluations/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Update evaluation (protected)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/evaluations/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "score": 5,
  "comments": "Updated after review"
}

### Update decision (protected)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/evaluations/{{id}}/decision
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "decision": "PASS",
  "decisionReason": "Meets criteria"
}

### Delete evaluation (protected)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/evaluations/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
